NAME

  IPC::Cache

DESCRIPTION
 
  IPC::Cache implements an object store where data is persisted across processes

REQUIREMENTS

  IPC::ShareLite version >= 0.06
  Storable version >= 0.607

INSTALLATION

  perl Makefile.PL
  make
  make test
  make install

USAGE

  see perldoc IPC::Cache



  

 
